        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Wrap up Hypermode's engagement with GrowthX, discussing final deliverables and performance insights.](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=0.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [44 articles published; 6 more to be completed today and published tonight](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=92.0)\n  - [Site performance dipped post D-Graph content migration; likely due to natural search volume fluctuations](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=105.0)\n  - [GrowthX to provide lessons learned and insights for potential future collaboration](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=215.0)\n  - [Slack channel to remain open until mid-next week for final communications](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=259.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Content Status and Handover\n\n  - [44 articles published to date](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=92.0)\n  - [6 more topics to be completed today and published tonight](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=95.0)\n  - [Jessica to retain access to Airtable and associated Google Docs](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=4.0)\n  - [Looker dashboard accessibility dependent on Google Search Console access](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=14.0)\n  - [Google Analytics not critical for Hypermode's tracking needs](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=30.0)\n\n### Performance Analysis\n\n  - [Overall website performance showing a slight decline after D-Graph content migration](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=105.0)\n  - [Hypothesis: Natural decline due to varying search volume, not competitor activity](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=136.0)\n  - [Specific metrics:](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=181.0)\n      - [Small bump in average positions across categories](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=181.0)\n      - [Small dip in Click-Through Rate (CTR)](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=181.0)\n  - [Potential factors for performance dip:](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=123.0)\n    1.  High traction on 3 specific articles previously, not replicated this week\n    2.  Possible site cannibalization due to undefined search space\n    3.  Temporary lag from publishing 3 articles weeks ago\n\n### Future Insights and Collaboration\n\n  - [GrowthX to provide:](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=215.0)\n      - [Lessons learned from the engagement](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=215.0)\n      - [Insights and guidance for potential future collaboration](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=241.0)\n      - [Key takeaways and early hypotheses](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=249.0)\n  - [Acknowledgment of short engagement and early stage of the space limiting full optimization](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=220.0)\n\n### Wrap-up Logistics\n\n  - [GrowthX to keep Slack channel open until mid-next week](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=259.0)\n  - [Final report to be shared via Slack and email](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=275.0)\n  - [GrowthX team available for future inquiries or potential re-engagement](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=284.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [GrowthX to complete and publish remaining 6 articles tonight](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=100.0)\n  - [GrowthX to compile and share lessons learned, insights, and key takeaways](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=249.0)\n  - [Jessica to ensure continued access to necessary tools (Airtable, Google Docs)](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=4.0)\n  - [Mara to notify before closing Slack channel mid-next week](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=280.0)\n  - [Team to finalize any remaining communications via Slack/email](https://fathom.video/share/yKpMVmsrBxs8JGgt8pty8YCakV6YQpms?tab=summary&timestamp=275.0)\n"
